.description
A 3D object editor with many features.  Has an easy to use interface with
many user selectable options.  The main view can be easily rotated,
positioned or scaled with the mouse, which makes the editor fast and
responsive.  Special features include fractals, multiply command, point and
click editing, an Arexx interface and much more.  
